{
  "stem": "17543.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 247.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think who was this sort look strong enough to do some work and might be survive longer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So those people will go first to the gas and then to the ovens who looked the thinnest and less fit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you see, I, I-- I'm just lucky I survived, because they never put tattoo on me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you know that they were Polish women who--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they were speaking Polish language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of these Polish women did speak a little Hungarian as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that they said, you know, where they-- where they come from.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where these is, some of these came from the names of the towns, which is family obviously, is town, like Cracow and, oh, I don't know, I, I recognized the names of those towns as belong to Poland.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, they said they are Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said polska, is mean Polish in Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I guessed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every barrack had two women who was responsible for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how they was, anyway-- to make sure we stay put where.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, course of the time we was in this place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Forever and ever had to stand on this side of the barrack, five by five behind one another for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These German soldiers came up and down, and kept on, I'm, I'm sure, watched it our numbers is there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, where could we go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway end of the evening, they was given a slice of, like, liver pate, [? little round ?] slice.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the supper, no bread, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we was inside, that was, we had to be crammed into these beds, these bunk beds, but there is nothing in it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's no blanket or anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
